{"3122910": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "我的AI女友", "steam_appid": 3122910, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122910/extras/d6a571480c0091d162ae8022a3e97e00.avif?t=1770693556\" width=614 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >男主角張俊失戀後，跟好友阿哲在酒吧喝悶酒，阿哲推薦他購買最新科技AI女友，望著阿哲那張縱慾過度的臉，原本對AI毫無興趣的張俊也不由心生好奇，本著嘗試看看的心情點開了產品訂購網站。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沒想到訂購過程卻頗為艱辛，因為不會下關鍵字，一開始不是生成奇美拉就是生成外星人，一番波折後，總算生成了個人模人樣的，他已經很累了，個性的部分就隨便亂點一通便送出了訂單。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隔天一早，張俊被門鈴聲吵醒，他的AI女友到貨了，還是個意想不到的貨，試用期30天，張俊能否和這貨成功走完30天呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122910/extras/da76985638fdce6f561baa8c2d49a1f2.avif?t=1770693556\" width=614 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主線劇情中有多次選項，每一次的選擇都將影響最終的結局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而隨著劇情發展將逐步開啟更多互動選項，從跟沫沫【聊天】、幫她【換裝】，到帶她去【充電】等等，你們的關係可能越來越親密，也可能無法磨合，好好選擇你的行動，努力提升跟她的【適配度】吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122910/extras/3df6877a9bf943138f2fcd6fd3609a2f.avif?t=1770693556\" width=614 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了和沫沫培養感情，玩家還可以去AI妓院嫖妓，只要選對購買的酒水量，就能跟超正的AI機器妓女做愛呦！努力賺錢來買酒吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122910/extras/f78312fcad1b2f3391eb5e5a2f51cfee.avif?t=1770693556\" width=614 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遊戲特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇16張全動態HCG，10張基礎CG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇遊戲文字8萬字</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇三位主要女角</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇輕鬆詼諧、日常養成向題材遊戲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇遊戲結局：3種(退貨、損壞、快樂結局)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122910/extras/3c42e3ecdb8eecd53c521b03c9e1ea7c.avif?t=1770693556\" width=614 height=346 /></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122910/extras/d6a571480c0091d162ae8022a3e97e00.avif?t=1770693556\" width=614 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >男主角張俊失戀後，跟好友阿哲在酒吧喝悶酒，阿哲推薦他購買最新科技AI女友，望著阿哲那張縱慾過度的臉，原本對AI毫無興趣的張俊也不由心生好奇，本著嘗試看看的心情點開了產品訂購網站。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沒想到訂購過程卻頗為艱辛，因為不會下關鍵字，一開始不是生成奇美拉就是生成外星人，一番波折後，總算生成了個人模人樣的，他已經很累了，個性的部分就隨便亂點一通便送出了訂單。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隔天一早，張俊被門鈴聲吵醒，他的AI女友到貨了，還是個意想不到的貨，試用期30天，張俊能否和這貨成功走完30天呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122910/extras/da76985638fdce6f561baa8c2d49a1f2.avif?t=1770693556\" width=614 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主線劇情中有多次選項，每一次的選擇都將影響最終的結局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而隨著劇情發展將逐步開啟更多互動選項，從跟沫沫【聊天】、幫她【換裝】，到帶她去【充電】等等，你們的關係可能越來越親密，也可能無法磨合，好好選擇你的行動，努力提升跟她的【適配度】吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122910/extras/3df6877a9bf943138f2fcd6fd3609a2f.avif?t=1770693556\" width=614 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了和沫沫培養感情，玩家還可以去AI妓院嫖妓，只要選對購買的酒水量，就能跟超正的AI機器妓女做愛呦！努力賺錢來買酒吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122910/extras/f78312fcad1b2f3391eb5e5a2f51cfee.avif?t=1770693556\" width=614 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遊戲特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇16張全動態HCG，10張基礎CG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇遊戲文字8萬字</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇三位主要女角</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇輕鬆詼諧、日常養成向題材遊戲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇遊戲結局：3種(退貨、損壞、快樂結局)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122910/extras/3c42e3ecdb8eecd53c521b03c9e1ea7c.avif?t=1770693556\" width=614 height=346 /></span></p>", "short_description": "抱著玩玩的心態決定嘗試一下，貨到時卻傻了眼，這…這個凶巴巴的+9妹就是我的AI女友？？？（黑人問號 本著客家精神，決定先留下她， 什麼！家務模組要課金？廚藝模組和性愛模組也是？！可惡也太死要錢了吧！ 雖然AI女友是資本主義的產物，卻也不是全無好處的，至於是什麼，就只能在遊戲中得知了~", "supported_languages": "繁體中文, 英文, 俄文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 泰文, 簡體中文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122910/3cd233f7041f1b22a9ef8a51ece0ec16aebea310/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1770693556", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122910/e77d330b79c5ea0aa85576ba08cbc0d127edaec4/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1770693556", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122910/e77d330b79c5ea0aa85576ba08cbc0d127edaec4/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1770693556", "website": "https://playmeow.com/", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br>